OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStaying dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud during Monday
OL,7,Fmorning. However, increasing amounts
OL,8,Fof sunshine are likely to develop into
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Rather mild, with
OL,10,Flighter winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy overnight and dry,
OL,13,Fwith some occasional breaks in the
OL,14,Fcloud. Winds becoming light and
OL,15,Fvariable with some fog patches
OL,16,Fpossible by the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
