OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTuesday will be dry with
OL,6,Flight winds. Cloudy for the most with
OL,7,Fsome occasional sunny spells during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Widespread fog patches
OL,9,Flikely overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FFoggy
OL,12,Fstart becoming cloudy with light winds
OL,13,Fon Wednesday. Morning fog will quickly
OL,14,Fclear on Thursday becoming cloudy
OL,15,Flater. Remaining cloudy on Friday with
OL,16,Fpatchy rain and drizzle.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
